Attention Frc Teams​:loudspeaker:

We have decided to share the SQL file containing the team details we collected with the color-crescendo project we did for Frc and the messages they want to give to the world, which includes 100+ teams

Detailed content of the file

100+ teams;

*postcode
*city
*country
*team number
*team name
*message they want to announce to the world
*date
*lat
*lon

such information is included.

example;
(‘07070’, ‘ANTALYA’, ‘Türkiye’, ‘7672’, ‘SCORPIONS ROBOTICS’, ‘uploads/1441asdasdasdasd.png’, ‘176.232.59.59’, ‘Peace at Home, Peace in the World’, ‘2024-02-27 19:01:56’, ‘36.8864752’, ‘30.7029585’)

Those interested can access the relevant file and more details from the following link:

github.com
